name: CI Global Infrastructure Private Pool
longDescription: The pool's investment objective is to seek to provide regular income and capital appreciation. In certain exchange-traded funds which utilize leverage in an attempt to magnify returns by either a multipleor an inverse multiple of a specified widely quoted market index , and certain ETFs that seek toprovide daily results that replicate the daily performance of gold or the value of a specified derivative, the underlyinginterest of which is gold on an unlevered basis, by a multiple of 200% .
